title: Topics in International Health (Wellcome-Trust)
description:
Topics in International Health


Topics in International Health is an excellently beautiful set of 14 Medical CDs released by Wellcome-Trust.

The topics covered by CDs are (Each topic in a separate CD)

1. Acute Respiratory Infection
2. Dengue
3. Diarrhoeal Diseases
4. HIV/AIDS Revised edition
5. Human African Trypanosomiasis
6. Leishmaniasis
7. Leprosy
8. Malaria 3rd edition
9. Nutrition
10. Schistosomiasis
11. Sexually Transmitted Infections 2nd edition
12. Sickle Cell Disease
13. Trachoma 2nd edition
14. Tuberculosis

For more information, please do visit
 <a href="
http://www.wellcome.ac.uk/About-us/Publications/CD-ROMs/Topics-in-International-Health/index.htm" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.wellcome.ac.uk/About-us/Publications/CD-ROMs/Topics-in-International-Health/index.htm</a>

Here for the first time ALL 14 CDs are provided. In addition, as a bonus you get following additional CDs provided by WHO.


15. Immunization in Practice
16. International Pharmacopoeia
17. Water Sanitation Health

An excellent volume for medical students, practitioners, doctors, microbiologists, clinicians and in general anyone who is interested in medical studies.

Enjoy! And please do not forget to leave a note of thanks! That is the only reward I get! And I am very happy with that.

Then please go out and treat your patients better!

May God bless all of us!!!!!!!
